## Install Nx Remix Plugin

{% aside type="note" title="Keep Nx Package Versions In Sync" %}
Make sure to install the `@nx/remix` version that is on the same minor version as the `nx` version in your repository. If the version numbers get out of sync, you can encounter some difficult to debug errors. You can [fix Nx version mismatches with this recipe](/docs/guides/tips-n-tricks/keep-nx-versions-in-sync).
{% /aside %}

```shell {% frame="none" %}
nx add @nx/remix
```

